assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Kuwait Real Estate Company K.P.S.C., a real estate company, owns, develops, and manages various properties in Kuwait. Its residential property management services include financing, valuations, market appraisals, sales, and acquisitions; and services to clients in retail market comprise search, advisory, sales and financial services, property and facilities management, project management, and consultancy services. The company also provides consultancy and transactional services, such as leasing, sales, site search, site feasibility, space analysis, space optimization, price negotiation, renewal, legal, etc. to owner, tenant, investor, or developer of commercial property. In addition, it undertakes the planning and development of new projects, which include financing, identifying, and implementing redevelopment opportunities, designing and undertaking the rehabilitation, and up gradation and repositioning of projects, as well as advice and transaction support services to clients in the hospitality segments. The company provides real estate services in the residential, retail, commercial, and hospitality services sectors. Kuwait Real Estate Company K.P.S.C. was incorporated in 1972 and is based in Safat, Kuwait.
